                            </handNote>
                        </handDesc>
                        <decoDesc ana="#decoration.object.helmet"><decoNote>A triple plumed helmet of the Montefortino type is engraved in the upper part of the tablet, in the pediment area and extending down between lines 1-3 of the text.</decoNote></decoDesc>
